Items.mt: When he said this, the king of thieves broke off his breath. The company's main business is to provide a wide range of products and services to the public. The first time I saw a bag of black mulberry stained with blood, I didn't take it.

Items.r: 说话这句话，贼王就断气了。{p}虽没找到宝藏，但意外的在贼王身上搜出一些钱。{p}还看到一袋沾满血的黑桑葚，就不拿了。
